UIStateTranferer is a simple framework 
that helps you write application(
especially simple or sample Swing app) 
in a state-centric way. It may helps 
you think clearly andreduce your coding
burden.

This pack contains:

package gameX:
	GameX -> a simple demo game using 
	this framework;

package net.flyingff.commons.ui:
	UIStateTransfer -> core class of 
	this framework;
	ActionListenerAdder -> a adapter
	class for JButton and Button

please contact me via ff@flyingff.net
